Third-party data
----------------
This work integrates data from:

  * Trafiklab / Samtrafiken GTFS Sweden 3 (public transit schedule
    and realtime feeds). Licensed under Creative Commons Zero (CC0)
    by the originating regional transit authorities.
    https://www.trafiklab.se/

  * OpenStreetMap contributors (street geometry, basemap tiles via
    CartoDB, building footprints via Overpass). © OpenStreetMap
    contributors, licensed under the Open Database License (ODbL).
    https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright

  * CartoDB raster tile styling, licensed under CC BY 3.0.
    https://carto.com/attributions

These datasets retain their original licenses and must be attributed
per their respective terms when redistributing this work or
derivatives thereof.
